      <p style="opacity:0.9;font-size:1.1rem;margin-bottom:2rem;">Check your WASA Rawalpindi water bill by 8-digit C-Code (Consumer Code).</p>
<p>PakistanBill.online is <strong>Pakistan's only platform</strong> with all three WASA utilities — <a href="/wasa-rawalpindi-bill/">WASA Rawalpindi</a>, <a href="/wasa-lahore-bill/">WASA Lahore</a>, and <a href="/wasa-faisalabad-bill/">WASA Faisalabad</a> — alongside all electricity, gas, and telecom bills. In Rawalpindi, also check your <a href="/iesco-bill/">IESCO electricity bill</a> and your <a href="/sngpl-bill/">SNGPL gas bill</a>. See all water bills on the <a href="/water/">water bills hub</a>, or see our <a href="/rawalpindi/">Rawalpindi utility bills guide</a>.</p>
